last_episode_to_air.name: The Toy Knight Returns!
last_episode_to_air.overview: Axel is fed up with being the kind, enthusiastic boy that everyone appreciates. He dreams of being a shadow hero, cold and lonely… which he finds much cooler!

name: Power Players
overview: A human who is able to transform into a toy-sized action figure recruits a team of toy heroes for adventures around the world.

episodes.name: Unboxing (1)
episodes.overview: Axel is staying with his Uncle who is a former toy inventor and current toy repairman. While playing with a collectors toy he breaks it. Going into his Uncles workshop he finds his uncles secret lab and some power bands. He releases the evil toy, Madcap who starts to smash everything. He discovers the power bands turn him into an action figure.

episodes.name: Unboxing (2)
episodes.overview: The other toys first attack him thinking he's working with Madcap but quickly find that he's one of them. They begin their battles to prevent Madcap from finding a power battery and making all toys evil. Sadly he escapes with the battery.

episodes.name: Attack of the Thermometron 9000
episodes.overview: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat improperly upgraded by Slobot as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

episodes.name: The Dynamo Dynamic
episodes.overview: Dynamo is sent by Madcap to capture Slobot. Axel, Sarge and Masko must stop him from being taken.

episodes.name: Access Denied
episodes.overview: The team messes with Sarge's new security system and the house is put on lockdown but not before ejecting all of them first, and they have Madcap to battle.

episodes.name: Swing Set Jet Set
episodes.overview: Galileo has traded Bearbarian's hammer for a jetpack with Princess Sugar Salt and she's destroying the park with it.

episodes.name: Side Kicked
episodes.overview: Masko and most of the Team, including Axel, are taken over by a bad toy named Pirate set by Madcap. It's up to Zoey to rescue all of them.

episodes.name: Porcupunk Rock
episodes.overview: Madcap turns to Axel and his team for help after a sonic upgrade to Porcupunk threatens to bring down the house.

episodes.name: All Trick No Treat
episodes.overview: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun – just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick ‘r’ treater of all, Madcap!

episodes.name: Iced Out
episodes.overview: Madcap’s latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

episodes.name: Gathering Dark
episodes.overview: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

episodes.name: Bobbie Not Blobby
episodes.overview: Axel discovers that the culprit behind Bobbie Blobby’s missing mech-suit is Masko, who only wanted to clean out its clogged clay cannons, but lets the suit fall into the hands (or tentacles) of Dr. Nautilus – intent on flooding the sewers!

episodes.name: Sand Trap
episodes.overview: Axel and the team take to the desert dunes of a playground sandbox as Madcap attempts to unearth an army of Spy Lizards from the same line as Galileo!

episodes.name: Dodge City
episodes.overview: Axel embraces the spirit of dodgeball to stop Madcap and Princess SugarSalt’s battle over who is the better villain from spilling over into Zoe and Cleo’s argument over who is the better coach!

episodes.name: The Best Team
episodes.overview: When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby, the team must stop the baddies and help Axel – stuck in a car with Luka – cross the finish line!

episodes.name: Joyride
episodes.overview: At a rummage sale with Uncle Andrew, Axel and Zoe must stop Madcap from turning her long-lost tank toy, Joyride, into an agent of mayhem!

episodes.name: Savage Axel
episodes.overview: Bearbarian helps Axel get in touch with his wild side as Orangutank "liberates" nature from an apartment building - tossing potted plants of all sizes out the window and onto innocent bystanders below!

episodes.name: The Scratch Pack
episodes.overview: Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.

episodes.name: Knockout
episodes.overview: Axel and the team juggle not waking Uncle Andrew from his nap and stopping Orangutank from stealing Andrew's latest invention: the Knockout Box!

episodes.name: Sarge in Charge
episodes.overview: Axel and the team must rescue Sarge Charge from a solo mission in the backyard, which Orangutank has turned into his own personal heart of darkness.

episodes.name: The Other Side
episodes.overview: Axel must 'save' Bobbie Blobby after she defects to Madcap's team, tempted by Porcupunk and his assertion that she belongs with the bad toys.

episodes.name: Bear-Knuckle Brawl
episodes.overview: Axel must team up with Bearbarian to stop Madcap from transforming Luka's stuffed bear collection into an invincible army.

episodes.name: Saving Private Masko
episodes.overview: Masko takes Axel's call for more discipline too seriously and loses sight of his own identity in the process, becoming a no-nonsense soldier set on toeing the line - and ill-equipped for a lucha libre with Madcap!

episodes.name: On Your Toes
episodes.overview: After a Porcupunk sighting, Axel leads a recon mission that slowly but surely proves to be a wild goose chase devised by Sarge, who's secretly pursuing a hobby that he's afraid to share with his teammates.

episodes.name: Friend Wars
episodes.overview: Princess SugarSalt dupes Axel into hanging out with Cleo LeBall and usurps his role as team leader, forcing Zoe to step in and keep the toys together.

episodes.name: That Slobot is No Bot of Mine
episodes.overview: Axel and the team compete against themselves in tests of skill, strength, and stamina, but when SloBot gets belittled, he splits into three separate robots - each with their own evil personalities!

episodes.name: Bowling for Ballers
episodes.overview: Axel and the team must intervene when Zoe's not-so-friendly bowling competition with Cleo LeBall gets interrupted by Madcap, Porcupunk, and their new cohort, the mischievously magnetic Dynamo.

episodes.name: Countdown
episodes.overview: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

episodes.name: Joke's On You, Bro!
episodes.overview: Axel and the team turn Galileo's camouflaging pranks around on him, convincing the gullible gecko that he's permanently invisible - to disastrous results!

episodes.name: Out Of My Head
episodes.overview: Axel must help Sarge and Bobbie learn to walk in each other's shoes - literally - after Luka unwittingly switches the toys' heads!

episodes.name: Freeze!
episodes.overview: Axel and his team find themselves in a tough position after Ice Crusher makes it too cold for them to fight back at full speed.

episodes.name: King Axel
episodes.overview: After a screening of the King Arthur tale, Axel holds out his sword and declares himself king, but when Dynamo uses his magnetism to steal the weapon and bestow it upon Masko, it casts doubt among the team over who is the true leader.

episodes.name: The Trojan Bear
episodes.overview: When Axel opens a subscription gift-box he didn't even order, the team finds their ranks divided by a robotic bear - or Princess SugarSalt in disguise!

episodes.name: Thirst For Power
episodes.overview: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

episodes.name: Party On
episodes.overview: As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher - Princess SugarSalt, who has turned the decorations and gifts into instruments of chaos!

episodes.name: Bringing Up Baby
episodes.overview: Zoe leaves Axel in charge of the school project - watching over an infant simulator doll - but when MadCap brings the doll to life, Axel and the team must stop the baby without damaging it or risk getting a failing grade!

episodes.name: Stretched Too Thin
episodes.overview: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

episodes.name: From Below
episodes.overview: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

episodes.name: Winner Takes All
episodes.overview: After months of training for Luchador Day, Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo!

episodes.name: Prepare For the Worst
episodes.overview: Axel and Bobbie Blobby skip out on Sarge's disaster-prep drills, leaving enough of a gap in the team's defenses for a crow to swoop in and snatch Sarge! Feeling responsible, Axel leads the team on a search-and-rescue mission.

episodes.name: Stuck On You
episodes.overview: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

episodes.name: Opposites Attract
episodes.overview: Claiming he's good at heart, Dynamo convinces Axel and the team to help him find a battery that can power his centrifuge and free him from Madtrap's control - but Bobbie Blobby isn't buying the baddie's story.

episodes.name: The Thing in the Wall
episodes.overview: When Axel and the team accuse Galileo of stealing their possessions, the lizard must hunt down the true culprit - a mysterious creature behind the wall - to prove his innocence.

episodes.name: Madtrap
episodes.overview: Madcap and Princess SugarSalt trap Axel and the team inside a Minergy-powered labyrinth that attacks them with their greatest fears, forcing them to work together and escape as a unit

episodes.name: To Tame the Perilous Skies!
episodes.overview: With Axel’s drone-wing broken, the team must find another way to stop Madcap and his minions as they take to the skies in toy airplanes for an aerial assault on the city park.

episodes.name: Four Color Fallout
episodes.overview: Axel, Galileo, and Sarge get Minergy-transported by Madcap into the pages of Axel’s favorite comic book, the hero of which turns out not to be so cool after all.

episodes.name: Grin and Bear It
episodes.overview: When a toothache sends Axel to the dentist, the team must fight off Princess SugarSalt, who confuses Axel’s new “crown” for the real thing.

episodes.name: Green with Envy
episodes.overview: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

episodes.name: Bring on the Bad Guys
episodes.overview: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

episodes.name: Spies Like Us
episodes.overview: Uncle Andrew warns Axel that his vintage “Agent Danger” action figure is off-limits, only to have the toy escape on its own! Axel and the team must return Danger to its rightful place before Uncle Andrew finds out.

episodes.name: Return of Thermometron 9000
episodes.overview: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

episodes.name: Just Like Robots
episodes.overview: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when he uses digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing them to act unpredictably in order to defeat him.

episodes.name: Drummed Out
episodes.overview: Under Axel's helpless gaze, a musical challenge opposes Galileo and Sergeant Charge. Guitar in hand, Porcupunk joins in the competition.

episodes.name: Go Big or Go Home
episodes.overview: Axel and the Power Players are bored and worried - there haven't been any bad toy attacks for several weeks -, and decide to go to Madcap's lair.

episodes.name: Weekend at Axels
episodes.overview: Madcap finds Joyride, whom he hires for a special mission: to seize Axel's Power Bandz! Will Joyride betray his group?

episodes.name: Things That Go Bump in the Night
episodes.overview: While Axel is in the middle of the night with Zoe and Luka, Madcap and his henchmen break into his home. The big bad has made his own Power Bandz!

episodes.name: Fetch
episodes.overview: Thinking of pleasing Axel, Slobot turns into a robot dog, but he behaves like a crazy young dog running around, all the way to Madcap's lair.

episodes.name: What's Wrong With Uncle Andrew?
episodes.overview: Uncle Andrew surprises the Power Players and Axel in the house, but does not react. What's going on with him? The investigation begins ...

episodes.name: Scratch My Back
episodes.overview: When Bearbarian's seam cracks, his back itches horribly. Finding nothing and no one to appease him, the teddy bear decides to wake up Zoe's three stuffed cats. It's the return of the Scratch Pack!

episodes.name: A Fistful of Minergy
episodes.overview: Madcap has created a weapon that removes Minergie from living toys, leaving them helpless! He comes to find Action Axel and his gang.

episodes.name: Serge Charge
episodes.overview: A Charge lookalike shows up with his big motorcycle: friend or foe?

episodes.name: The All-New-All-Different Power Players?!
episodes.overview: The Power Players are captured by Ruffin, the Toy Thief. To deliver them, Axel brings together a new team of Power Players made up of: Joyride, the Scratch Pack, Bot-Guy, and Zoe. Will these recruits be able to accomplish their mission?

episodes.name: Operation: Midnight
episodes.overview: Ruffin stole Luka's teddy bears and sells them at a flea market. The Power Players will take advantage of the night to recover them.

episodes.name: That's the Spirit!
episodes.overview: Uncle Andrew promised Axel that he would give him a toy if he helped him at a charity sale. Impatient and eager to pick out a toy, Axel descends into the store overnight. But strange events will happen there ... Axel will understand that giving is better than receiving.

episodes.name: Pyrant Park
episodes.overview: While Axel plays with his friends in the park, the Pyrant pyramid makes a new appearance, determined to no longer control the minds of toys, but that of humans!

episodes.name: Ajar
episodes.overview: In Madcap's absence, Sarge Charge has taken the lead of the wicked toys. He orders them to go and throw a very heavy box at the city dump ...

episodes.name: Jungle Boogie
episodes.overview: Bearbarian has disappeared. Axel finds him at the bottom of the garden, but his companion is now teaming up… with Orangutank.

episodes.name: Take Cherge
episodes.overview: Slobot finds Sergeant Charge K.-O. in the garden; the latter had his new minergie tracker binoculars stolen. Who could have committed this crime? Axel is convinced he has the answer.

episodes.name: Bot Out
episodes.overview: Madcap wakes up robots from a video game. They are not aggressive but have only one objective… to wreak havoc in the city!

episodes.name: The Most Fun Ever
episodes.overview: Axel and Madcap are jealous of the super collector robot that Luka plays with. Everyone will want it for themselves!

episodes.name: Hot Pursuit
episodes.overview: Porcupunk and Dynamo have recovered Axel's mobile phone he had registered on turning into a toy! A chase begins in the streets of the city ... quickly before Axel's secret is revealed to the world!

episodes.name: On the Wrong Track
episodes.overview: Slobot finds Sergeant Charge K.-O. in the garden; the latter had his new minergie tracker binoculars stolen. Who could have committed this crime? Axel is convinced he has the answer.

episodes.name: Maxel & Adcap
episodes.overview: Due to a plan by Madcap linked to the powers of minergie, Axel ends up in Madcap's body… and Madcap in Action Axel's body!

episodes.name: Remote-Controlled Chaos
episodes.overview: Joyride would like to join the Power Players, but they are very busy playing with a remote control car - which is not lost on Madcap ...

episodes.name: Selfie!
episodes.overview: Galileo keeps filming himself for his admirers. Axel reminds him of all the times this lack of attention has hurt his friend...

episodes.name: The Toy Knight Returns!
episodes.overview: Axel is fed up with being the kind, enthusiastic boy that everyone appreciates. He dreams of being a shadow hero, cold and lonely… which he finds much cooler!

episodes.name: Big Mad Part 1
episodes.overview: While Axel would like to grow up to be taken more seriously, MadCap creates a huge body that allows him to gain immeasurable strength. The Power Players seem destitute in the face of this immense threat ...

episodes.name: Big Mad Part 2
episodes.overview: Axel will do everything to defeat Madcap who has become giant and overpowered. What if he asks Uncle Andrew for help?
